{
  "stem": "12674.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "All I saw was a bunch of people which I had been respecting and everything going like lambs to the slaughter and saying, yes, sir, and yes, sir, and yes, sir.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was very, very disturbing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was working like a dog, and-- and I wasn't allowed to go to school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- and-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it was a very hard-- and you could-- I-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It never occurred to me that this was going to last for as long as it did.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But then again, I was young and stupid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I didn't know whatever what I was dealing with.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I didn't understand politics.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "All I knew is that-- that I was in a living-- I was living in a nightmare, and there was no thing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And my-- my father, he managed to keep my brother with him and taught him, you know, with working.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he got himself-- through some connections, he got himself assigned to a-- a-- a carpentry shop, and he was working there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the-- the head of the Gestapo in Vienna was a-- the Jewish-- of the Jewish department, the-- the Jewish [NON-ENGLISH] but the Jewish department of the Gestapo in Vienna, was a man named Kuchman, and he-- my father had done his villa.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And when he became the big shot, when there were lists made for-- for people being sent away to concentration camp, we were not on them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Most of the people were sent in '41 and '42.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They had transports of 1,000 people.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
